Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you saved me. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guiche! Where are you hiding?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.24,0:16:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guiche!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reinard already told me that you were part of the peeping!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why isn't Tabitha wearing anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.23,0:17:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please, don't hold me any closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found Guiche!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.23,0:17:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.43,0:17:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.12,0:17:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're scared of ghosts?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'm with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.27,0:17:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tabitha.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.93,0:17:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, this is turning me on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Forgive me, Montmorency.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:57.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was on impulse. Just a whim!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.13,0:18:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time around, I really know what kind of person you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.28,0:18:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.72,0:18:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ball for dolls?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.71,0:18:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could dance with you if you want. {S1 ep6}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been working hard to this day, wishing to see her smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,yet why doesn't it ever work out?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:35.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe you. {S1 ep6}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.48,0:18:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Obviously, I'm at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:43.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it was Tiffa's request, I did something to betray Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet I say I haven't done anything wrong, but I've hurt Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.02,0:18:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.30,0:19:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dolls dance here every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.59,0:19:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you were in that hole, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.44,0:19:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to deny it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.19,0:19:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't know that I was being taken to peep on the girls' bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.08,0:19:28.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I tagged along since they said there was something good to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.91,0:19:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course, you don't believe what I say, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, you're not smart enough to lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you well.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.82,0:19:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, even about Tiffa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll believe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.07,0:19:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:20:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if you were asked, it's your fault for actually doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm sorry, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise never to touch any other girl's breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.11,0:20:11.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Even though you like big ones?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer small ones like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.69,0:20:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop throwing me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.91,0:20:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.54,0:20:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always wanted to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.54,0:20:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to kiss me to make up for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.22,0:20:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Most certainly, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.30,0:21:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.85,0:21:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It... It looks like you really do like small ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a reason for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.43,0:21:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like girls smaller than Louise either!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.68,0:21:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby pledge not to touch the breasts of others!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.86,0:21:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.27,0:21:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can touch mine, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.19,0:21:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You know what happens i-if you break the pledge, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.11,0:21:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.67,0:21:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.56,0:22:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.44,0:22:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.96,0:23:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's wrong with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My chest is aching. My body is trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.23,0:23:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what love is?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.21,0:23:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero no Tsukaima. Princess no Rondo.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.13,0:23:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Taboo Magic Potion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.27,0:23:37.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.26,0:23:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you if you look away.
